🚀 Tunnel Rush Unblocked Extension 🌌

Dive into the high-speed 3D tunnel adventure! Play Tunnel Rush directly in your Chrome browser and navigate through dizzying twists and turns!

Features:

🏎️ Speed through endless 3D tunnels
🎯 Challenge your reflexes and precision
🌈 Experience vibrant graphics and dynamic obstacles
Installation Guide:

Click 'Add to Chrome' to begin the installation.
Find the Tunnel Rush icon on your Chrome toolbar after installation.
Click the icon whenever you wish to start your high-speed adventure!
Uninstallation Guide:

Right-click the Tunnel Rush icon on your toolbar.
Choose 'Remove from Chrome'.
Confirm your choice by clicking 'Remove'.
